lead_paragraph: Embattled Gary Neville, never shy of an opinion as player or pundit, is tired of listening to his own voice as he tries to arrest Valencia's slide in his increasingly gloomy first foray into management.

headline.print_headline: Winning, Not Talking, Only Way to Win Over Valencia Fans-Neville
headline.main: Winning, Not Talking, Only Way to Win Over Valencia Fans-Neville
